{{ template "chart.sourcesSection" . }}

## Installation

```bash
helm install minecraft-operator-crds \
  oci://ghcr.io/lexfrei/minecraft-operator-crds \
  --version {{ template "chart.version" . }} \
  --namespace minecraft-operator-system \
  --create-namespace
```

## Upgrade

```bash
helm upgrade minecraft-operator-crds \
  oci://ghcr.io/lexfrei/minecraft-operator-crds \
  --version NEW_VERSION \
  --namespace minecraft-operator-system
```

## Uninstall

> **Warning:** Uninstalling CRDs will delete all PaperMCServer and Plugin custom resources!

```bash
helm uninstall minecraft-operator-crds \
  --namespace minecraft-operator-system
```

## CRD Reference

### PaperMCServer

```yaml
apiVersion: mc.k8s.lex.la/v1alpha1
kind: PaperMCServer
metadata:
  name: my-server
spec:
  updateStrategy: "auto"
  # ... see documentation
```

### Plugin

```yaml
apiVersion: mc.k8s.lex.la/v1alpha1
kind: Plugin
metadata:
  name: my-plugin
spec:
  source:
    type: hangar
    project: "Author/Plugin"
  # ... see documentation
```

